            <p class="bd-final-eyebrow">The full definition</p>
            <p class="bd-final-sentence">The Bitcoin <em>network</em> is the <em>open</em>, <em>permissionless</em>, <em>decentralized</em>, <em>secure</em> <em>protocol</em> &mdash; <em>bounded by energy</em>, <em>absolutely scarce</em>.</p>
            <div class="bd-final-reflection">
                <p>Eight words. Each one load-bearing. None of them ornamental.</p>
                <p>Remove any one and you no longer have Bitcoin &mdash; you have something else, weaker in a specific, instructive way. The coherence and alignment of these properties is what produces the money.</p>
                <p>This is why Bitcoin is not just the first ideal money the world has known. By the same logic, it is also the last.</p>
